snippet.title: Amber Heard Abused Johnny Depp #JusticeForJohnnyDepp
snippet.description:
As I had always expected and as increasing evidence has shown, Amber Heard was indeed the abuser, not Johnny Depp. 

Sources:
https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7053927/Johnny-Depp-accuses-Amber-Heard-severing-finger-hurling-bottle-vodka-him.html
https://www.eonline.com/uk/news/771265/amber-heard-s-ex-girlfriend-tasya-van-ree-speaks-out-following-domestic-abuse-allegations
https://www.cosmopolitan.com/uk/entertainment/news/a44291/winona-ryder-defends-johnny-depp-domestic-abuse-allegations/
https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7947733/Amber-Heard-admits-hitting-ex-husband-Johnny-Depp-pelting-pots-pans-tape.html

Graphics by RoyaltyFreeTube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pvomDfQmhWQ&list=PLn9YX2V-0CpGoPxKKBP-eonghp6bpRb8O&index=2&t=0s

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #MeToo
